        <abstract>
            <para>Records of vascular plants, bryophytes and lichens collected in July 2024 from 250 m² forest plots in Hurdal, Gran, Østre Toten and Nannestad (Akershus &amp; Innlandet, Norway). Data were gathered using the Nature in Norway 3.0 mapping protocol as part of the project “Biodiversity Mapping of Forests From Above (BioDivAbove)”. </para>
        </abstract>
