        <methods>
            <methodStep>
                <description>
                    <para>Twenty-nine 250 m² plots were surveyed using the Nature in Norway 3.0 vegetation mapping protocol. Vascular plants, lichens and bryophytes observed within each plot were noted as presence. Mobile GNSS equipment was used for coordinates and elevation.</para>
                </description>
            </methodStep>
